data.description: Another masterful renovation approved by the HRP: Queen Lane has all new interior and amenities found in today's new construction. New insulation and new energy efficient windows throughout; new high efficient 7500 BTU centralized heating and air condition systems, cherry wood cabinetry, micro-wave, stainless steel refrigerator, all new 200amps electrical service, all new plumbing throughout, ceiling fans in all bedrooms, recess lighting throughout first, beautiful ceramic tile baths with all new fixtures, gleaming hardwood flooring on first, and beautiful berber carpet on second. This home is a must see for your discriminatory buyer/s that will not settle for nothing less than the best. Must be a 1st time homebuyer; property must be principle residence; homebuyer/s must have income less than 80% of median, or 115% of the median income (depending on the underling source of the program) adjusted for family size. Housing counseling required.
